                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features-sub-grid">
                    <div class="features">
                        <h3>Features</h3>
                        <ul style="list-style-type:circle;" class="overlay-points">
                            <li>Create projects with your teams</li>
                            <li>Manage your tasks and clearly visualize the progress of each</li>
